Show HN: Build your own GPT-powered daily newsletter bot with AI Newsie
text:
Meet AI Newsie, a news aggregator bot that summarizes and speaks the latest articles from the New York Times.

Built entirely in Rust, the bot uses OpenAI's GPT-3 to generate concise summaries of each article, AWS Polly to create a text-to-speech recording, and Sendgrid's API to send the recording via email to recipients.
